    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in such incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. If you're looking for that perfect, 'good as new' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
