    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is\u2014it's been my absolute pride and joy. It has been babied since day one and seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a single scratch or ding to be found, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It drives like a total dream and I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
