      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of atmospheric performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double VANOS system ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the rev range. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential, providing visceral mechanical feedback. This chassis remains structurally pristine with documented subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings. Every component, from the Sachs dampers to the cross-drilled rotors, reflects a standard of maintenance that preserves the original kinematic precision. The exterior retains its high-luster finish with no signs of clear coat failure or oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear.",
